cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper proposes an approach to transfer control policies learned in simulation onto a real robot for a manipulation task. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a pairwise loss function to adapt control policies from simulation to reality. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is relevant as the paper uses depth images as the main form of sensor input. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper proposes a method to transfer learned policies from simulation to reality. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with control policies for a robotic system.
